---
---

<header class="hud">
  <div class="hud__score">Mesafe<span id="score">0 m</span></div>
  <div class="hud__score">Süre<span id="time">60.0</span></div>
  <div class="hud__score">Rekor<span id="best">0 m</span></div>
  <button id="restart" class="hud__btn" type="button">Yeniden başla</button>
</header>
<div class="board-wrap">
  <canvas
    id="stage"
    width="480"
    height="380"
    aria-label="Gösterge paneli"
  ></canvas>
  <div id="overlay" class="overlay" role="dialog" aria-live="polite">
    <div class="overlay__inner">
      <h2 id="overlay-title">Vites</h2>
      <p id="overlay-msg">
        Manuel vites — gaza basıp motoru çalıştır, devir 5500'e yaklaşınca
        E ile vites yükselt. Yanlış viteste motor zorlanır; redline'da
        2 saniye kalırsan motor patlar. 60 saniyede en uzak yolu kat et.
      </p>
      <button id="overlay-btn" class="hud__btn" type="button">Başla</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="pedals" aria-hidden="false">
  <button id="btn-brake" class="pedal pedal--brake" type="button" aria-label="Fren">FREN</button>
  <button id="btn-down" class="pedal pedal--gear" type="button" aria-label="Vites indir">−</button>
  <div class="pedal pedal--gear pedal--readout"><span id="gear-readout">N</span></div>
  <button id="btn-up" class="pedal pedal--gear" type="button" aria-label="Vites yükselt">+</button>
  <button id="btn-gas" class="pedal pedal--gas" type="button" aria-label="Gaz">GAZ</button>
</div>
